# SmartFlow CRM - Frontend Design System

## Design Language

### Core Principles
```
1. Minimalistic & Clean
   - Ample white space
   - Clear visual hierarchy
   - Reduced visual noise
   - Purposeful animations

2. Glassmorphism Elements
   - Subtle transparency
   - Blur effects (backdrop-filter)
   - Light borders
   - Soft shadows

3. Modern & Professional
   - Sharp corners with selective rounding
   - Consistent spacing
   - Clear typography
   - Smooth transitions
```

